hadiths[31]{hadithnumber,text}:
4204,"Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi musalman ko , jiske paas kuchh ho aur wo usmein wasiyat karna chahta ho, is baat ka haq nahi ke wo 2 raatein ( bhi) guzaarey magar is tarah ke uski wasiiyat uske paas likhi hui ho."
4205,"Abda bin Sulaiman aur Abdullah-bin-Numair donon ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, albatta un donon ne kaha : uske paas (maal (ho jis mein wasiiyat karey ( qaabil wasiiyat maal ho. (aur is tarah nahi kaha : jis mein wasiiyat karna chahta ho. (mafhoom wahi hai, alfaz ka farq hai.)"
4206,"Ayub , Yunus , Usama-bin-Zaid Lesi aur Hisham bin Sad sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ubaidullah ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur un sab ne kaha : uske paas koi ( aisi ( cheez hai jis mein wo wasiiyat kare. albatta Ayub ki hadis mein hai ke unhon-ne kaha : wo usmein wasiiyat karna chahta ho Ubaidullah se Yahya ki riwayat ki tarah ."
4207,"Amr-bin-Haris ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : kisi musalman aadmi ke liye, jiske paas koi ( aisi ( cheez ho jis mein wo wasiiyat karey, ye jaaiz nahi ke wo teen raatein ( bhi) guzaarey magar is tarah ke uski wasiiyat uske paas likhi hui ho. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman suna hai mujh par aik raat bhi nahi guzri magar meri wasiiyat mere paas maujood thi."
4208,"Yunus , Aqeel aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath Amr-bin-Haris ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4209,"Ibrahim bin Sad (bin Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Aamir-bin-Sad aur unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hijjatul-wada ki mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisi bimari mein meri iyaadat ki jiski wjah se main maut ke kinarey pahunch chuka tha. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! mujhey aisi bimari ne aa liya hai jo aap dekh rahe hain aur main maaldaar aadmi hon aur sirf aik beti ke siwa mera koi waaris nahi ( banta .) to kya main apne maal ka 2 tehai hissey sadqa kar dun? aap ne farmaya : nahi. maine kaha : kya main iska aadha hissey sadqa kar dun? aap ne farmaya : nahi, ( albatta ( aik tehai ( sadqa kar do (aur aik tehai bahut hai, bila shubah agar tum apne warison ko maaldaar chhod jao to ye us se behtar hai ke unhein mohtaaj chhod jao, wo logon ke samney dast sawal daraaz kartey phirein , aur tum koi cheez bhi kharch nahi kartey jiske zariey se tum Allah ki raza chahtey ho, magar tumhen iska ajr diya jata hai yahan tak ke us luqmey ka bhi jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein daltey ho. kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! main apne sathiyon ke (Madina lot janey ke baad) peechhey ( yahin Makka mein) chhod diya jaaunga ? aap ne farmaya : tumhen peechhey nahi chhoda jaeyga, phir tum koi aisa amal nahi karogey jiske zariey se tum Allah ki raza chahtey hogey , magar uski bina par tum darjey aur bulandi mein (aur ( badh jaogey aur shayad tumhen chhod diya jaey ( lambi umr di jaey) yahan tak ke tumharey zariey se bahut si qaumon ko nafa miley aur dusri bahut si qaumon ko nuqsan pahunchey . aey Allah ! mere sathiyon ke liye unki hijrat ko jari rakh aur unhein unki eidiyon ke bal wapas na lota , lekin be chaarey Sad bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu) (wo to faut ho hi gaey. ( kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us wjah se unke liye gham ka izhar afsos kya ke wo (is se pahley hi ( Makka main ( aa kar) faut ho gaey they."
4210,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Yunus aur Mamar sab ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
4211,"Sad bin Ibrahim ne Aamir-bin-Sad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat karne ke liye mere yahan tashrif laey. padhi. aagey Zohri ki hadis ke ham mana bayan kya aur unhon-ne Sad bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman ka tazkira nahi kya, magar unhon-ne kaha : aur wo (Hazrat Sad bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu)) na-pasand kartey they ke us sarzameen mein wafat paaein jahan se hijrat kar gaey they."
4212,"Zuhair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Samak-bin-Harab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Musab-bin-Sad (bin abii-waqaas ( ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main bimar hua to maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas paigham bheja , maine kaha : mujhey ijazat dijiye ki main apna maal jahan chaahoon taqseem kar dun. aap ne inkar farmaya, maine kaha : aadha maal ( taqseem kar dun? (aap ne inkar farmaya, maine kaha : aik tehai ? kaha : ( mere ( aik tehai ( kehney (ke baad aap khamosh ho gaey. (eik tehai ki wasiiyat se aap ne mana na farmaya magar iske barey mein bhi ye farmaya : aik tehai bhi bahut hai. hadis : 4215 , 4214 ( kaha : iske baad aik tehai (ki wasiiyat ( jaaiz ghahrii ."
4213,Shoba ne Samak se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne ye bayan nahi kya : iske baad aik tehai (ki wasiiyat ( jaaiz ghahrii .
4214,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne Musab-bin-Sad se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri iyaadat ki to maine kaha : kya main apne sarey maal ki wasiiyat kar dun? aap ne farmaya : nahi. maine kaha : to aadhey ki? aap ne farmaya : nahi. maine kaha : aik tehai ki? to aap ne farmaya : haan , aur tehai bhi zyada hai."
4215,"abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne hamein Ayub sakhtiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman Himyari se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke) das se zayed mein se) teen beton ( Aamir , Musab aur Muhammad ( se riwayat ki, wo sab apne walid se hadis bayan kartey they ke Makka mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iyaadat karne ke liye Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif laey to wo roney lagey, aap ne puchha : tumhen kya baat rulaa rahi hai? unhon-ne kaha : mujhey dar hai ke main is sarzameen mein faut ho jaaunga jahan se hijrat ki thi, jaisey Sad-bin-khaula (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! Sad ko shifa de. aey Allah ! Sad ko shifa de. teen baar farmaya, unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mere paas bahut sa maal hai aur meri waaris sirf meri beti baney gi, kya main apne sarey maal ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ne farmaya : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : do tehai ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : nisf (aadhe) ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : aik tehai ki? aap ne farmaya : ( haan ( aik tehai ki) wasiyat kar do (aur aik tehai bhi zyada hai. apne maal mein se tumhara sadqa karna sadqa hai, apne ayaal par tumhara kharch karna sadqa hai aur jo tumharey maal se tumhari biwi khaati hai sadqa hai aur tum apne ahal aur ayaal ko) kafi maal de kar) khair ke aalem mein chhod jao. padhi. ya farmaya : ( achi ( guzraan ke sath chhod jao. padhi. ye us se behtar hai ke tum unhein us haal mein chhodo ke wo logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein aur aap ne apne hath se ishara karke dikhaya."
4216,"hamein Hammad ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne Amr-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman Himyari se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke teen beton se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) Makka mein bimar huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki iyaadat karne ke liye unke yahaan tashrif laey. padhi. aagey Saqafi ki hadis ke ham mana hai."
4217,"Muhammad ne Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey hazrat-Sad-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke teen beton ne hadis bayan ki, unmein har aik mujhey apne doosrey sathi ki tarah hadis bayan kar raha tha, kaha : Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) Makka mein bimar huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey. padhi. aagey Humaid Himyari se Amr-bin-Saeed ki hadis ke ham mana hai."
4218,"Esa-bin-Yonus , Wakee aur ibne-Numair sab ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kaash! ! log tehai se kam karke chothai ki wasiyat karein kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai : tehai ( tak ki wasiiyat karo) , aur tehai bhi zyada hai. Wakee ki hadis mein bada hai ya zyada hai ke alfaz hain."
4219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : mere walid faut ho gaey hain, unhon-ne maal chhoda hai aur wasiyat nahi ki, agar (ye maal ( unki taraf se sadqa kar diya jaey to kya (ye ( unki taraf se kaffara banega ? aap ne farmaya : haan."
4220,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Hazrat Aaisha se khabar di ke aik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : meri walida achcha wafat pa gain , mujhey unke barey mein yaqin hai ke agar wo baat kartin to sadqa kartin, agar main unki taraf se sadqa kar dun to kya mere liye ajr hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan."
4221,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki ke aik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! meri walida achcha faut ho gaee hain aur wasiyat nahi kar sakein , mujhey unke barey mein yaqin hai ke agar wo kalam kartin to zaroor sadqa kartin, agar main unki taraf se sadqa kar dun to kya unke liye ajr hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan."
4222,"abu-Usama , Shuaib-bin-Ishaq , Rooh-bin-Qasim aur Jafar-bin-Aun , sab ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. abu-Usama aur Rooh ki hadis mein hai : kya mere liye ajr hai? jis tarah Yahya-bin-Saeed ne kaha, aur Shuaib aur Jafar ki hadis mein hai : kya unke liye ajr hai? jis tarah ibne-Bishr ki riwayat hai,"
4223,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab insan faut ho jaey to uska amal munqata' ho (kat) jata hai. siwaey teen amal ke (wo munqata' (khatm) nahi hotey ( : sadqae jaariya ya aisa ilm jis se fayda uthaya jaey ya nek betaa jo uske liye dua kare.
4224,"sulaim-bin-akhzar ne hamein Ibne-Aun se khabar di, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein zamin mili, wo iske barey mein mashwara karne ke liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey khaibar mein zamin mili hai, mujhey kabhi koi aisa maal nahi mila jo mere nazdeek is se zyada umda ho. to aap mujhey iske barey mein kya hukm detey hain? aap ne farmaya : agar tum chaho to uski asl waqf kar do aur us (ki aamadni ( se sadqa karo. kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey (is shart ke saath) sadqa kiya ke uski asl na bechi jaey, na usey khareedaa jaey, na wirsey mein hasil ki jaey aur na hiba ki jaey. kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us (ki aamadni) ko fuqaraa , aqrabaa , ghulaamon, Allah ki rah , musaafiron aur mahmaanon mein sadqa kiya aur (qarar diya ke) us shakhs par koi gunah nahi jo iska nigraan hai ke wo ismein maaldaar baney baghair Maruf (bhaley) tareeqey se usmein se khud khaaey ya kisi dost ko khilaey. (Ibne-Aun ne) kaha : maine ye hadis Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( ko bayan ki, ''jab main us jagah par maaldaari haasil kiye baghair pahuncha'' to Muhammad ne (un alfaz ke bajaey) maal jama kiye baghair ke alfaz kahey. Ibne-Aun ne kaha : mujhey us shakhs ne khabar di jisne is kitab ( likhe huey wasiyat-naamey) ko padha tha ke usmein maal jama kiye baghair ke alfaz hain."
4225,"ibne-abi-Zayda , azhar samaan aur ibne-abi-Adi sab ne Ibne-Aun se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, albatta ibne-abi-Zayda aur azhar ki hadis Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke us qaul par khatm ho gaee : ya maaldari hasil kiye baghair kisi dost ko khilaey. iske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kiya aur ibne-abi-Adi ki hadis mein wo qaul hai jo Suleim ne zikr kiya ke maine ye hadis Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( ko bayan ki, aakhir tak."
4226,"Sufiyan ne Ibne-Aun se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey khaibar ki zaminon se aik zamin mili, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : mujhey aik zamin mili hai, mujhey kabhi koi maal aisa nahi mila jo mujhey is se zyada mahboob aur mere nazdeek is se zyada umda ho. padhi. unhon-ne un sab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur unhon-ne , maine ye hadis Muhammad ko bayan ki, , aur uske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kiya."
4227,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hamein Maalik-bin-Mighwal se khabar di aur unhon-ne Talha-bin-musrif se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wasiyat ki? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. maine puchha : to musalmanon par wasiyat karna kyon farz kiya gaya hai ya unhein wasiyat ka hukm kyon diya gaya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (tarkey ko taqseem karne ki wasiiyat nahi ki balke) Allah Taala ki kitab (ko apnaaney , amal karne) ki wasiyat ki."
4228,"Wakee aur ibne-Numair donon ne Maalik-bin-Mighwal se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta Wakee ki hadis mein hai : maine puchha : to logon ko wasiyat ka kaisey hukm diya gaya hai? aur ibne-Numair ki hadis mein hai : maine puchha : musalmanon par wasiyat kaisey farz ki gaee hai?"
4229,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Muawia donon ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu-Waeil se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne na koi Dinar tarka mein chhoda na dirham , na koi bakri , na oont aur na hi aap ne (is tarah ki) kisi cheez ke barey mein wasiyat ki."
4230,Jarir aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4231,"Aswad-bin-Yazeed se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : logon ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas zikr kiya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) wasi ( jisey wasiyat ki jaey) they. to unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Kab wasiyat ki? bila shubah aapko apne seeney se.  ya kaha : apni god se. sahara dene wali main thi, aap ne bartan mangwaya, iske baad aap ( kamzori se) meri god hi mein jhuk gaey aur mujhey pata bhi na chala ke aap ki wafat ho gaee, to aap ne unhein Kab wasiyat ki?"
4232,"hamein Saeed-bin-Mansoor , Qutaiba-bin-Saeed , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr Naqid ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Saeed ke hain. padhi. sab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Sulaiman ahwal se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jumerat ka din , aur jumerat ka din kaisa tha ! phir wo roney lagey yahan tak ke unke aansuon ne pathar ke tukron ko tar kar diya. maine kaha : Ibne-Abbas ! jumerat ka din kya tha? unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka marz shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaya to aap ne farmaya : mere paas ( likhney ka saman ( lao , main tumhen aik kitab ( tahreer ( likh dun taake tum mere baad gumrah na ho. to log jhagad padey , aur kisi bhi Nabi ke paas jhagadnaa munasib nahi. unhon-ne kaha : aap ka kya haal hai? kya aap ne bimari ke zere asar guftgu ki hai? aap hi se iska mafhoom poochho ! aap ne farmaya : mujhey chhod do, mein jis haalat mein hun wo behtar hai. main tumhen teen chizon ki wasiyat karta hun : mushrikon ko jazeera Arab se nikal dena aur aaney waley wufood ko isi tarah atiye dena jis tarah mein unhein diya karta tha. ( Sulaiman ahwal ne) kaha : wo ( Saeed-bin-Jubair ( teesri baat kehney se khamosh ho gaey ya unhon-ne kahi aur main usey bhool gaya. Abu-Ishaq Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Hasan-bin- Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
4233,"Talha bin Musrif ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : jumerat ka din, jumerat ka din kaisa tha! phir unke aansu bahney lagey yahan tak ke maine unke donon rukhsaaron par dekha maano motiyon ki ladi ho, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere paas shaaney ki haddi aur dawaat laao. padhi. ya takhti aur dawaat. padhi. main tumhen aik kitab (tahreer) likh dun, iske baad tum hargiz kabhi gumrah na hogey. to logon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimari ke zer asar guftgu farma rahe hain."
4234,"Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ka waqt qareeb aaya, ghar mein kuchh aadmi maujood they, unmein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere paas aao, main tumhen aik kitab (tahreer) likh dun, iske baad tum gumrah nahi hogey. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par takleef aur dard ka ghalba hai aur tumharey paas Quran maujood hai, hamein Allah ki kitab kafi hai. is par ghar ke afraad ne ikhtilaf kya aur jhagad padey, unmein se kuchh keh rahe they : (likhney ka saman) qareeb lao, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen kitab likh dein taake iske baad tum kabhi gumrah na ho. aur unmein se kuchh wahi keh rahe they jo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha. jab unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas zyada shor aur ikhtilaf kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uth jao. Ubaidullah ne kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : yaqinan museebat thi badi museebat jo unke ikhtilaf aur shor ki wjah se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke wo tahreer likhney ke darmyan haail ho gaee (ke aap kitabat na kara sakey.)"
